M|launch-strategy|1. What are you launching? (New product, major feature, minor update)
M|launch-strategy|2. What's your current audience size and engagement?
M|launch-strategy|3. What owned channels do you have? (Email list size, blog traffic, community)
M|launch-strategy|4. What's your timeline for launch?
M|launch-strategy|5. Have you launched before? What worked/didn't work?
M|launch-strategy|6. Are you considering Product Hunt? What's your preparation status?
